item.title: Head Icons Why it dosnt work
item.dc:creator: @silabsoft RuneAgent
item.description:
@silabsoft wrote:

The reason head icons do not work is that we though it was smart to take newer caches and put them in a old deob. Although it compiles and runs we do loose some information in the process. Head icons is one of them. here is why.

in deob 317 you will find


for(int j4 = 0; j4 < 20; j4++)
                    aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1Array1095[j4] = new Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1(class44_2, "headicons", j4);

however we use i think 370 cache which reads like this


            for(int k4 = 0; k4 < 6; k4++)
                headIcons_PK[k4] = new Sprite(streamloader2, "headicons_pk", k4);

            for(int l4 = 0; l4 < 9; l4++)
                headIcons_Prayer[l4] = new Sprite(streamloader2, "headicons_prayer", l4);

            for(int i5 = 0; i5 < 6; i5++)
                headIcons_Hint[i5] = new Sprite(streamloader2, "headicons_hint", i5);

so with a few small changes, i dont believe i have to go into detail sense your all community members.

[br][size=1]Posted on: March 08, 2007, 08:39:08 PM[/size][hr]then for a bit of fun try flipping the mapfunctions and types
